
------------------------------------------------------------
ableP - alpha release 1
- major reworking and reorganization of previous unreleased version
- covered Promela from SPIN version 6.0.1
- uses new style scope rules
- embedded C code and new version 6 features implemented as extensions
  to the host:core language
- type checking functionality implemented as an extension.  This
  demostrates how ETCH-like analysis could be done this way.  Minimal
  checking is currently done however.

------------------------------------------------------------

ableP - previous unreleased version.
- covered Promela from SPIN version 4.2.9
- handled inlining in a more traditional manner
- parses embedded C code using the ableC grammar
- basic syntax and 4.2.9 style scope rules
